  "title" : "Does a finally block run even if you throw a new Exception?",
  "body" : "<p>In this code will <code>someVar</code> be set even if the catch block is executed and the second Exception is thrown?</p>\n\n<pre><code>public void someFunction() throws Exception {\n    try {\n        //CODE HERE\n    } catch (Exception e) {\n        Log.e(TAG, \"\", e);\n        throw new Exception(e);\n    } finally {\n        this.someVar= true;\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
